{"tid":2347540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登仔不願面對]美國係隻紙老虎","createTime":"2020-12-31T06:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T06:45:50.000Z","uid":275238,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e6e106c084fa4e635e5ac7ecc517495f10a436","tid":2347540,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"本來只係毛魔鳩噏嘅口號但近年睇到已經變咗做事實<br />\n自越戰之後已經畏首畏尾唔敢再直接介入任何野，只會口頭警告同埋制裁下做騷，列根後嘅總統更加只係個口水佬，鄧小平一早睇穿晒所以先夠膽打越南8964吞香港，水鳩美國佬滲入國際組織如世貿世衛玩撚到出晒面美國佬仲on99繼續俾佢撚，任由中共南海起島同武力鎮壓新疆香港，依家連總統都俾人收買埋仲未識死，拜登上場後更加唔洗旨意會出手，我係中共都唔會驚依隻紙老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1c7f24c629769e5a60a87aca66d0d7c9845ffb","tid":2347540,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dea58e165294cf6e1d82e4c7ecec5359ba6e694","tid":2347540,"uid":42340,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:31:12.000Z","msg":"個啲咩淫權法簽完做過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26f16d6e387b9ca99bb74a4cb712e315fdb1a2f","tid":2347540,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:32:17.000Z","msg":"打伊拉克果D叫乜？"},{"pid":"56744690ee36e3968e40216801cc1974332e64ec","tid":2347540,"uid":387001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T06:45:50.000Z","msg":"姐係全世界都係紙老虎"}]}